title: Arctic Monkeys - Straighten The Rudder + Unplugged
description:
Straighten The Rudder and my collection of unplugged songs.

Neither of these uploads are official releases, they're just made by fans.

Straighten The Rudder was made by someone on Tumblr. It's a collection of acoustic Arctic Monkeys songs from youtube, some of the songs are poor quality but i'm not complaining.

The unplugged album  contains 8 songs, a lot better quality than Straighten The Rudder. It has some songs from AM and a few from Straighten The Rudder but they're a higher bit rate.

enjoy and please seed!
